William Forster

M, #744981, d. 10 January 1574

Last Edited=9 Nov 2022

William Forster was the son of Sir Humphrey Forster and Elizabeth Sandys. He married Jane Hungerford, daughter of Sir Anthony Hungerford and Jane Darrell, circa 1553.1 He died on 10 January 1574.1

He held the office of High SHeriff of Berkshire in 1569.1 He held the office of Member of Parliament (M.P.) for Berkshire in 1572.1

Child of William Forster and Jane Hungerford

Prince Ghazi bin Muhammad1

M, #744986

Last Edited=17 Sep 2022

Prince Ghazi bin Muhammad was born on 15 October 1966 at Amman, Jordan.1 He is the son of Prince Muhammad bin Talal and Firyal Ishaid.1 He married, firstly, Areej Zawawi on 4 May 1997.1 He and Areej Zawawi were divorced in 2021.1 He married, secondly, Miriam de Ungria y Lòpez, daughter of Bernardo de Ungria y Goibarri and Carmen Lòpez Oleaga, on 3 September 2022.1
